Text:
The volume for these changes from soft-as-fuck to blow my eardrums out.
Song changed and I damn near shat myself.

Warning to those who download this, the settings for volume are all messed up. For some reason when you import these to iTunes, or whatever, some get set to play at volume -100%, and others volume +100%.
When you load these files into iTunes, select them all, right-click and go to "Get Info", then "Options" and set the volume adjust to "none". Your ears will thank you.
